high_descs: Turn around and approach a sidetable on your left from the side where you can access its drawer
Take a spatula out of the sidetable's drawer.
Leave the room via exit in the upper right corner, turn right and walk straight to a sink on the other side.
Put the spatula in the sink, rinse it out, and take it back out
Move back to the room you came from, and stop next to the sidetable
Place the spatula on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the rinsed-out spatula on th sidetable.
